  <brief_title>Task-Oriented Aerobic Exercise Training in Chronic Stroke Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Task-Oriented Aerobic Exercise Training on Cardiorespiratory Fitness and Cerebral Blood Flow in Chronic Stroke Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
